                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Discovered in&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-6684&quot; title=&quot;Support casting values with bytes schema to string &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-6684&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-6684&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, the converter is using week date year (YYYY) instead of plain year (yyyy) and day in year (DD) instead of date in month (dd).&lt;/p&gt;

